{
  "texts": [
    "The participants were invited to participate in the study through social media groups and pages.",
    "The interviews were conducted offline and online using Zoom, Microsoft Teams, and Google Meet.",
    "The researchers took notes while interviewing the participants.",
    "In the subsequent analysis stage, we utilized inductive coding and thematic analysis methodologies as outlined by Braun and Clarke (2006) and Fereday and Muir-Cochrane (2006).",
    "This method facilitates flexibility in finding themes and concepts."
  ]
}